PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F347A1672342499
OL,6,FThen, were terrestrial TV to be facing
OL,7,Fclosure, a full support scheme would be
OL,8,Fnecessary for those who might be left
OL,9,Fbehind.
OL,11,FThis is not unusual.
OL,13,FFor years some in the radio industry
OL,14,Fhave wanted FM radio switched off. But
OL,15,Fsignificant numbers are yet to be won
OL,16,Fover by digital radio, BBC Sounds and
OL,17,Fother ways of listening.
OL,19,FEven turning off AM is easier said than
OL,20,Fdone.
OL,3,CAn internet-only BBC and ITV ditching
OL,4,Cits PSB status: how likely?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G5/12
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
