OL,6,FSimilarly, just over a decade ago great
OL,7,Fefforts were made to help the elderly
OL,8,Fand vulnerable through digital
OL,9,Fswitchover ` long after most of us
OL,10,Fwondered what all the fuss was about.
OL,12,FThe concern was about more than access
OL,13,Fto technology. It was a fear, for
OL,14,Finstance, that those with poor eyesight
OL,15,For memory loss might find the simple
OL,16,Foperation of the equipment hard. Turn
OL,17,Fon your TV and digibox, switch to a
OL,18,Fparticular input then find your
OL,19,Fchannel.
OL,3,CAn internet-only BBC and ITV ditching
OL,4,Cits PSB status: how likely?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G6/12
