OL,6,FBefore you can imagine "Digital
OL,7,FSwitchover Ii" a prerequisite would be
OL,8,Fa portal with the simplicity of the EPG
OL,9,F` bringing all the available services
OL,10,Ftogether, with guaranteed prominence
OL,11,Ffor the BBC and other public service
OL,12,Fbroadcasters.
OL,14,FThis is a different question to whether
OL,15,Fthe licence fee should be replaced with
OL,16,Fa household charge.
OL,18,FMeanwhile some civil servants are
OL,19,Fworried ITV could pull out of public
OL,20,Fservice broadcasting.
OL,3,CAn internet-only BBC and ITV ditching
OL,4,Cits PSB status: how likely?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G7/12
