OL,6,FThe risk is that ITV could conclude
OL,7,Fthat the benefits of being on Channel 3
OL,8,F` prominence and guaranteed spectrum `
OL,9,Fare not worth the costs.
OL,11,FThese costs include:
OL,13,
OL,14,F Investing in programmes, notably
OL,15,Fnational and regional news, which do
OL,16,Fnot lead to a commercial return.
OL,17,F Tighter rules on the overall amount
OL,18,Fof advertising.
OL,19,F Being unable to broadcast the main
OL,20,Fservice in the STV area.
OL,3,CAn internet-only BBC and ITV ditching
OL,4,Cits PSB status: how likely?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G8/12
