OL,6,FMinisters and Ofcom do need to reach
OL,7,Fdecisions soon on the future licensing
OL,8,Fof Channel 3 and Channel 5.
OL,10,FBut ultimately nearly everything ITV
OL,11,Fshows is driven by its commercial
OL,12,Finterests, even if it also has wider
OL,13,Feconomic and social value.
OL,3,CAn internet-only BBC and ITV ditching
OL,4,Cits PSB status: how likely?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G9/12
