OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F347A1672342499
OL,6,FThe real debate is about what programme
OL,7,Fobligations are realistic after the
OL,8,Fcurrent Channel 3 licences run out and
OL,9,Fabout advertising volumes.
OL,11,FIn particular what regional news
OL,12,Fservices will be provided and what
OL,13,Flevel of wider provision is sustainable
OL,14,Ffor Wales, Northern Ireland and Border
OL,15,FScotland.
OL,17,FBut I fully expect ITV 1 to be on
OL,18,FChannel 3 and 103 on Freeview,
OL,19,Fsatellite and cable for the next 10
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,3,CAn internet-only BBC and ITV ditching
OL,4,Cits PSB status: how likely?
